creator: Animega
descriptionHtml:
Animega is a social network and chat platform for anime and manga fans. Download the new social media for otakus!

✔️ UNITE with anime, manga, cosplay and Tokyo Ghoul fans. Enter a world just for anime enthusiasts.
✔️ DISCOVER other anime fans who share your favorites and collaborate on posts.
✔️ ENGAGE with other anime fans and cosplayers to ask, answer, and discuss all the greatest anime scenes, anime game videos, anime characters, episodes and more.
✔️ SHARE your anime cosplay costumes, anime drawing and anime experiences from conventions and other events.
✔️ CHAT with cool anime fans all around the world. Make otaku friends.
✔️ CREATE your own profile with your anime and manga lists.
✔️ CREATE anime communities and share the latest anime trends. Invite your otaku friends to join in your community!

Animega is the best anime social networking app for your phone! Join in otaku's social media. 🔥

We are working for new updates for you. Your thoughts are very important to us. If you need any help, please contact us on hello@animega.co!

Follow us:
https://www.instagram.com/animegaco
descriptionShort: The best social network for Anime, Manga, Cosplay and Tokyo Ghoul Fans & Geeks!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We continue to develop Animega for you. Your feedback is very important to us. We are waiting for your feedback!

* UI&UX improvements.
* Feeds are separated.
* You can now send anime gifts to the people you want.
* You can access many features with Animega Coin.
* Bugs fixes.

We will continue to make new updates for you.
